---
title: Pork Rissoles & Roast Kūmara Chunks with Burger Sauce & Celery Slaw
description: Juicy pork rissoles, crispy roasted kumara, and a crunchy, tangy celery slaw—this meal is packed with flavour! Serve it all with a side of creamy burger sauce for the perfect finishing touch. There you have it - comfort food with a fresh twist!
